Peppers / capsicum and chillies - pretty fruits and small flowers, bright leaf colours, variety of fruit colours{"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8d/Grow-a-Decorative-Vegetable-Garden-Step-2Bullet11.jpg/v4-460px-Grow-a-Decorative-Vegetable-Garden-Step-2Bullet11.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8d/Grow-a-Decorative-Vegetable-Garden-Step-2Bullet11.jpg/v4-760px-Grow-a-Decorative-Vegetable-Garden-Step-2Bullet11.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
